text: Khandelwal bhai, tera naam toh goel hazaron baar leta tha, lekin apni mulakaat last sem tak ho hi nahi paayi. IITK ka highest package, isse hi mujhe andaza lag gaya tha ki tu kitna chapu hoga. text:
Bakait bro, apan toh destined soulmates hai yaar ğŸ¤. SOC saath me, Sumo Logic saath me, woh katne ke baad AlphaICs saath me, aur ab Zomato bhi saath me. Keep up the good work bro, bohot aage jaega tu. Hum chote logon ko bhool mat jana bas.

author: Abhijaat Ashish Kotamkar

text:
Campus ka pehla din yaad hai, meri teri aur pandey ki pehli mulakaat. Us din jab mujhe pata chala ki tu chess khelta hai tab mujhe laga ki koi nubda hoga jo maze ke liye khelta hoga. Lekin fir pata chala ki national ka banda hai aur 1700 rating. Meri toh gaand hi fat gayi, ki BC IIT me har koi chess me chapu hota hai kya? Us pehle din se leke campus ke aakhri din tak apan ne itne memories banaye hain ki try karun toh bhi saare na yaad kar paun.  Covid tak toh apan almost poore time hi saath rahete the. Room pe saath me, SOC me saath me, 3 inter-IITs pe saath me, baki colleges ke sports fests pe saath me aur kabhi kabaar lounge jana hua toh woh bhi saath me.
	First year me toh apan roomies hi the, aur itne aalsi ki room se nikalte bhi nahi the. Us saal toh apan ne itne chutyape kiye ki saare yaad bhi nahi. Bas apan dono hi toh shareef bachche the uss samay, jo gaali nahi dete the. Yaad hai B-top Indian Idol ke auditions, aur guard ka room pe aake ajeeb awazon ke baare me poochna ğŸ˜‚. Aur tere Yashika ke saath wale chats dekh kar jo hamari gaand fatti thi. Mini-militia me teri wajah se hare bomb hi ban karne pade ğŸ˜‚. Woh toh campus ka best year tha mere liye. Fir second aur third year me halaki apan alag rooms me ho gaye lekin pada toh main tere hi room pe rehta tha. Kabhi Tharwani se bachne toh kabhi Najan ki bitching karne. Aur saath me pada hua rehta tha Shrotria. Teri aur Shrotria ki aashiqui ke kisse maine hi toh failaye the. Apna banaya hua viral video yaad hai na? Itna viral ki tere ghar walon tak hi pohoch gaya ğŸ˜‚. Woh video dekhna hai yaar mujhe, abhi bhi pada hoga toh bhejna bro.
	Aur inter-IITs aur sports fests ko kaise bhool sakte hai. Inter-IITs me apan char aur ek senior, har baar yahi combination. Aur fir team ko carry mujhe karna padta tha ğŸ˜‚. Inter-IIT ki wajah se hi toh tera pclub wala talent hamare saamne aa paya tha. Woh photo abhi bhi mere liye chess team ke favourite photo hai. Ab tere talents ki baat chid hi gayi hai toh aur bhi gina hi deta hoon. Pehla toh tera jag prasiddh Goelâ€™s logic. Is logic se na jane kitne arguments ki maut hui hai. Agar koi ekdum hi hara hua argument ko jeetna ho toh woh tu hi jita sakta tha. Aur bhai teri baatein, aaj bhi apne random chats dekhta hoon toh bohot hasi aati hai ki BC ye kaisi baatein chal rahi hai. Aur teri paise bachane ki ninja technique ko kaise bhool sakte hai. Agar cheejein khareedoge hi nahi toh saare paise bach jaenge, tere iss philosophy ne mujhe bohot influence kiya hai. Najan ka banglore me bohot paisa bachne wala hai.
	Wing ke saath koi bhi cheej karni ho toh tu pehle nahi bolta tha. Fir tujhe baith ke manao. Aur ye zimmedari mujhe hi uthani padti thi. Sach bol raha hoon, zindagi me jitna main kisi ladki ko nahi manaunga utna tujhe mana chuka hoon.
	Placement ke din bhi main kabhi nahi bhoolunga. Kya questions baat dete the apan, kya strategies tayar karte the. Aur itna sab chutyapa karne ke baad bhi shortlists nahi nikalte the. Aur tu toh interviews ke liye baith bhi nahi paaya ğŸ˜‚. Fir hagne ke baad jinke shortlists aa rahe the unki mil ke bitching karte ğŸ˜‚. Aur placement se yaad aaya topo. Maine toh usme haat hi upar kar diye the, tum log dhoondo main toh bas chapunga. Maza aaya usme bhi.
	Yaar waise dil ka bohot achcha aadmi hai tu, kabhi mat badalna. Best of luck for the future bro. Touch me toh apan rahenge hi. Kabhi kuch khareedna hoga toh call laga dena, mil ke khareedne ka decision cancel kar denge.

P.S. - Bade company me job lagi hai, ab toh kharch karna seekh jana
P.P.S. - Kitna manau aur saale, aaja mlbb pe
author: Abhijaat Ashish Kotamkar

text:
Mujhe yaad hai apni pehli significant mulakat 2nd year me hui thi, jab apan dono goel ke room me pade rehte the ğŸ˜‚. Tere aur Goel ki aashiqui ke charche toh campus bhar famous hai. Tu aur Goel assignment karte waqt keede karne me bohot maza aata tha mujhe. Tere saath hang out karne me bada maza aata tha. Mafia khelte waqt toh aur bhi jyada, marne ke baad bhi chup hi nahi baithta ğŸ˜‚. God se toh yuhi pange lete rehta. Aur monopoly me bhi kya maza aata tha yaar. Assignment, class sab kuch chod ke monopoly khelne aa jata main. Aur placement ke woh din toh koi kaise hi bhoolega. Quant wala part toh tere hi bharose nikalta tha. Itna chutyapa karne ke baad bhi shortlists nahi nikalte the. Fir mil ke jinke shortlists aa rahe the unki bitching karte ğŸ˜‚. Aur uske baad aaya topo. Maine toh usme haat hi upar kar diye the, tum log dhoondo main toh bas chapunga. Maza aaya usme bhi. Dil ka bohot achcha aadmi hai tu, bas aise hi rehna. All the best for the future man, aur touch me rehna.

P.S. - Saale tera abhi bhi pizza ka 180 ka udhaar chukana baaki hai. Sahi bola tha goel, tere se paise wapas lena namumkin hai.

text:
Campus ka pehla din yaad hai, apan teeno aur apne parents ki mulakaat hui thi. Tab mere papa ne mujhe bola tha ki woh pandey achcha bachcha lag raha hai, uske saath gumna. Little did he know... dheere dheere tere asli rang saamne aane lagenge. Aisi aisi aawazein nikalta ki sis guard ki bhi gaand fat jaati. Itni bakchodiyan ki uss saal ki chahoon toh bhi saare yaad nahi kar paaunga. Yaad hai B-top Indian Idol ğŸ˜‚. Tera audition tape ab tak hai mere paas. Aur jo Goel ke chaatein padh ke jo apni gaand fat jaati thi. Woh mera campus ka favourite year tha.
	Fir second aur third year me halaki apne rooms alag ho gaye, par pada toh main tere hi room pe rehta tha. Raat me mujhe bhagane ke liye mehnat karni padti tum logon ko ğŸ˜‚. Aur teri zindagi toh waise bhi mere saamne khuli kitaab hi toh thi. Kahi kat jata ya kabhi chaap deta toh aake mujhe batata. Mujhe bhi tere life ki bollywood kahani sunne me kaafi maza aata. Achcha storyteller hai tu. I wish Mondey had worked out.
	Aur tera defining trait kaise bhool jaaunga, teri atyadhik gandagi. Tera 1 mahine nahi nahane ka record sahi main astounding hai. Aur furniture ka toh tera poora hi paisa bach jaega. After all, tere kapde (both washed and unwashed), khana, dabba, mobile, headphones aur baaki saari cheejein toh ek hi table pe manage ho jaengi. Lockdown me jab mere maa-baap safai ke liye meri gaand maarte the tab me tere gandagi ke anya kisse unko sunata aur woh mujh par â€˜chalo pandey se to achcha hi haiâ€™ karke thodi rehm dikhate.
	Aur crypto yaad hai? Apne assignments karne me tere se jyada madat toh Bakait ne kar di thi ğŸ˜‚. But NLP me carry karke tune uski bharpai kar di. All things aside, all the best for the future man, although I donâ€™t think you need it, I know youâ€™ll be successful. Bohot mazedaar aadmi hai tu, badalna mat. Aur haan, touch me rehna saale.

P.S. - Congrats on increasing the average package for placementsâ€™2020, Mr. OPC.
P.P.S. - Arey tera cocain wala video abhi tak mere paas pada hua hai, fb check karte rehna, just in case.

text:
So many memories bro, kahan se chalu karun? First year me apan marathi-marathi karke baat karte the (I did not know Mugal even existed back then). In logon ki gaand fat jaati thi jab apan marathi me bolte the. Insecure saale. Lekin apni achchi jaan pehchan toh SOC ke dauraan hi hui. Itni achchi ki apan roomies hi ban gaye.
	Starting me toh mujhe yaad hai apni bilkul nahi banti thi, atleast roommates ke perspective se. Baaki logon ko ek doosre ki bitching karte rehte ğŸ˜‚. Fir apan gradually ek doosre se accustom hue aur zyada close aae. Yaad hai apan kabhi kabhi raat me light band karke bed pe pade hue bas baatein karte the. Tu mujhe tere ambitious plans batata aur mujhe mera passion dhoondne ke liye push karta. Aur apne Tharwani se bachne ke liye banae hue masterplans, kya din the woh. Mujhe yaad hai thandi me tu din bhar bed par razai odhkar pada rehta, sirf hagne mootne ke liye uthta. Khana bhi skip, tere hibernating skills sahi me mind blowing the.
	Tu hamesha rote rehta tha na ki main tujhe courses me madat ke liye due credit nahi deta, ye le aaj de deta hoon. Mujhe countless courses me carry karne ke liye thanks a lot bro. Tune mujhe explore karna sikhaya, mere horizons expand kiye. Tere bina main titos me un ladkiyon se kabhi baat nahi kar pata, kabhi omegle nahi try karta, shayad Goa bhi nahi jaata. Iske liye, aur kahin aur counless cheejon ke liye, thanks bro.
	Najan yaar, itne saalon me tera nickname kabhi nahi pada. I truly liked â€™Shivaji ka left tattaâ€™ ğŸ˜‚, but it never caught on. Everything aside, in saalon me tere saath rehne me bohot maza aaya aur bohot seekha main. You are one of the most courageous and definitely the most confident person Iâ€™ve met till now. All the best for the future bro, go follow your dreams. Aur touch me toh apan rahenge hi.

P.S. - Isi season legend pohoch jaate hai ryuzaki, sab ki gaand fat jaegi!
